library(tidygraph)
library(ggraph)
library(tidyverse)
library(gtools)
library(hrbrthemes)
library(igraph)
library(RColorBrewer)

x<- read_csv("billboardHot100_1999-2019.csv")
# paliekamas tik paskutinis kartais kai daina chartino
y<- x %>%
  distinct(Artists,Name,.keep_all = TRUE)
y<- y %>% filter(lubridate::year(Week)>2010) %>% filter(Artists!="Jack, Jack")

y <- y %>% mutate(Artists = str_replace(Artists,"Tyler, The Creator","Tyler The Creator"))
y<- y %>% mutate(Genre = str_replace(Genre,"Hip-Hop","Rap"),
                 Genre = str_replace(Genre,"R&;B","R&B"),
                 list_of_artists = str_split(Artists,", "),
                 list_of_genres = str_split(Genre,",")) %>% 
  replace_na(list(Peak.position=-1)) %>%
  mutate(Peak.position = if_else(Peak.position==-1,Weekly.rank,Peak.position),
         weight = 100-Peak.position)

artists<- distinct(as_tibble(unlist(y$list_of_artists)))

genres<- unnest(y,col=list_of_genres) %>% count(list_of_genres) %>% arrange(desc(n))
genres<- genres$list_of_genres

artist_genre<- unnest_longer(y,col=list_of_genres) %>% unnest_longer(col=list_of_artists) %>%
  group_by(list_of_artists,list_of_genres) %>% count() %>% ungroup() %>% 
  group_by(list_of_artists) %>% slice_max(n,n=1) %>%
  arrange(factor(list_of_genres,levels=genres)) %>% slice_head(n=1)

artist_genre$list_of_genres <- fct_lump_n(artist_genre$list_of_genres,6)
artists<-left_join(artists,artist_genre,c("value"="list_of_artists"))
artists<- artists[1:2]

y<- y %>% filter(lengths(list_of_artists)>1)
weights <- map2(y$weight,y$list_of_artists,~rep(.x,choose(length(.y),2)))
name<- map2(y$Name,y$list_of_artists,~rep(.x,choose(length(.y),2)))
edges<-map(y$list_of_artists,~combinations(length(.x),2,.x))
edges<- reduce(edges,rbind)
edges <- as_tibble(edges)
edges$weights <- reduce(weights,c)
edges$Name <- reduce(name,c)

graph<-tidygraph::tbl_graph(nodes=artists,edges = edges,node_key = c("V1","V2"),directed = F)
g<- discard(to_components(graph),~gorder(.x)<5) # panaikinu mazas komponentes
g<- bind_graphs(g)
g<-g%>%
  activate(nodes) %>% 
  mutate(degr = centrality_degree(),
         degr_weighted = centrality_degree(weights=weights),
         clust = as_factor(tidygraph::group_louvain(weights = weights)),
)

g<- g %>%
  morph(to_split,clust) %>%
  activate(nodes) %>%
  mutate(main = ifelse(centrality_degree() == max(centrality_degree()),value,""),
         ) %>%
  unmorph()


g<- g %>% 
  activate(nodes) %>%
  mutate(list_of_genres = fct_recode(list_of_genres, "Ispan\u0173\nkalba"="En Espa\\xc3\\xb1ol",
                                     "Kantri"="Country","Kiti"="Other",
                                     "Hiphopas"="Rap"))

ggraph(g) +
  geom_edge_link0(aes(width=100-weights),edge_colour="grey66",show.legend=FALSE)+
  geom_node_point(aes(size=degr,color=list_of_genres))+  
  geom_node_text(aes(filter=(degr>5|main!=""),label=value),
                 family="Roboto Condensed",repel = TRUE,size=7)+ 
  theme_graph(base_size=22,title_size = 26,subtitle_size = 20) +
  scale_size(range=c(8,17)) +
  scale_edge_width_continuous(range=c(0.1,2)) +
  scale_color_brewer("Å½anras",palette="Paired",
                     guide=guide_legend(override.aes = list(size=6),
                                        nrow=1,title.position="top"))+ guides(size="none") +
  theme(legend.position="bottom") +
  labs(title="Visos muzikos atlik\u0117j\u0173 bendradarbiavimas",subtitle="Pagal Å¾anrus")
